{"tid":1093922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"富昌邨女子晾衫墮樓 送院搶救不治","createTime":"2019-04-06T02:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T07:51:47.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"285a37a836140c3331825653c417ed36ea2e5cbf","tid":1093922,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"深水埗富昌邨富誠樓，早上7時12分，一名婦人由高處墮下，倒卧地上昏迷。保安員發現致電報警，由救護員到場將事主送院搶救，但告不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓劉59歲，警方在現場調查，10樓單位的窗打開，該處沒有窗花，簷篷有一件紅色衣物，地下有死者的拖鞋，初步懷疑她晾衫時失平衡墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n晾衫墮樓意外過去時有發生，為保安全，晾衫時應遵從兩大安全守則，第一是要「腳踏實地」，切勿站在凳仔上晾衫；第二是堅持「伸手不伸人」，身體不能多於四分一伸出窗外，免失重心墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190406/59455602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190406%2F59455602&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=4b5ea6a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190406%2F59455602&h=94ffedc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190406/59455602</a>"},{"pid":"aa4c1a9575b6f57a28e37577ec6d74aa68662cc3","tid":1093922,"uid":4273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"【12:00】警方經調查後，相信女事主因病厭世墮樓，事件無可疑"},{"pid":"fb588db9d7654961b307c9930047a7e4ebbaa846","tid":1093922,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0eb4d634feb1225eb400745c5bfd7bdb80f6b8c6","tid":1093922,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"晾衫真係要帶安全帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bbbc0c907356631bdbfb65ab2dcd583d6a7e33","tid":1093922,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"一啲安全意識都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea